Ingredients:

100g/3½oz sourdough starter
500g/1lb 2oz ‘00’ flour, plus extra for dusting
10g/⅓oz fine sea salt
20ml/4 tsp olive oil, plus extra for greasing
coarse semolina, for scattering

For the topping:

500g tin plum tomatoes
extra virgin olive oil
250g/9oz mozzarella, broken into small pieces
1 bunch basil, leaves only
salt and freshly ground black pepper
1 spicy pepper

